    <h2>Welcome to Acquia CMS</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="text-section">
        <p>Acquia CMS is an opinionated instance of Drupal that enables Acquia customers to build beautiful websites
          without writing code.
        </p>
        <p>It provides an easier way to:</p>
        <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Build Drupal sites</li>
          <li>Manage their look & feel</li>
          <li>Create & manage content</li>
          <li>Integrate easily with products in the Acquia platform</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <p>Acquia CMS comes bundled with a demonstration website which will provide an ‘out-of-the-box’ experience
          which will demonstrate the power of Drupal and the Acquia DXP.
        </p>
        <p>What will this tour guide me through?</p>
        <p>This tour will guide you through key concepts of ACMS which will help your journey building with
          Drupal on the Acquia platform. It will also link you to more in-depth documentation and training materials
          within Acquia Academy, our learning platform.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="button-section">
        <a class="button button--primary" href="/admin/tour/dashboard">Get started</a>
